    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We take a little bit of liberty sleeping in and an even slower morning. There is no harm in resting the body when it will allow one to enjoy the day even more. Jordan and I fiddle around on her laptops for a bit and I do some writing and then oh my god it’s midday. We pack our big bags and head over to Dave and Molly’s house where we will be staying for the weekend. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
