      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Jordan has a sleep. I have a lovely catchup with Dave. He makes us some negroni’s and we sit outside on the little balcony beside the garden. Dinner poses potentially going out or making a pasta at home - we opt for the latter and all walk down the nearby grocery for ingredients. Dave whips it up and Molly seduces me into drinking Prosecco with her. To warm up the room Molly lights a fire on Youtube. ",
            "link": null
