    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The Stirrups seems to be a centrepiece for the South African contingency within London that have congregated here to recreate a Cape Town party. It’s quite hilarious actually. The music doesn’t inspire much dancing at first and we explore. Adam show us the smoking area downstairs and we find several half naked people covered in lumo paint outside. It appears that there is another party here.",
            "link": null
          },
