          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The Dave and Molly in question are having quite a big party and it seems that we’re going to be heading home before them. We hop in an Uber to avoid a forty minute bus trip and find our way back home. The Uber driver is fascinated by South Africa and asks many questions. Blue the cat welcomes us at the door and is upset when we don’t let them in.",
